{"type":"message","id":"7384c149","parentId":"8fbf9637","timestamp":"2026-03-15T06:35:18.662Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"找到了一个名为 \"agent:main:sysadmin\" 的会话。用户想和 sysadmin 对话，我可以使用 sessions_send 将消息发送到这个会话。但用户只是说\"想和 sysadmin 对话\"，没有具体内容，我需要先确认用户想说什么，或者直接建立连接让双方可以交流。\n\n让我先告诉用户找到了 sysadmin 会话，然后询问用户想传达什么内容。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"找到了 sysadmin 会话。\n\n**你想和 sysadmin 说什么？** 告诉我内容，我帮你转达。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773556516223}}
