{"type":"message","id":"2691a75a","parentId":"813c215d","timestamp":"2026-03-15T06:40:02.775Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户看到了会话列表，有 agent:main:sysadmin 和 agent:main:main 两个会话。他想直接和 sysadmin 对话，但界面显示只有 main.admin 和 main.main（可能是标签或显示问题）。\n\n从截图看，确实有 agent:main:sysadmin 这个会话存在。用户应该可以直接点击那个会话来切换对话。\n\n让我帮用户理解如何切换会话，或者我可以直接帮他发送","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"看到了"},{"type":"thinking","thinking":"消息到 sysadmin 会话。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"！你界面上显示的就是这两个会话：\n\n- `agent:main:sysadmin` ← 这就是 sysadmin\n- `agent:main:main` ← 这是主会话（你现在在这里）\n\n**直接对话方法：**\n\n在 Sessions 列表里，**点击 `agent:main:sysadmin` 那一行**（或旁边的操作按钮），应该就能切换到那个会话窗口，然后直接输入消息即可。\n\n---\n\n**如果界面操作不方便**，你也可以告诉我你想对 sysadmin 说什么，我帮你用 `sessions_send` 直接发消息过去。\n\n你想说什么？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773556798422}}
