{"type":"message","id":"c5e69f37","parentId":"e6a1e76c","timestamp":"2026-03-15T06:42:29.043Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说 workspace-sysadmin 不是 CEO 模板，让我检查一下。我需要先找到 workspace-sysadmin 的位置，然后读取里面的配置文件。\n\n当前工作区是 C:\\Users\\28964\\.openclaw\\workspace，workspace-sysadmin 可能是同级目录或者子目录。让我先探索一下目录结构。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9ca6998edc4b4e04a58f08aa","name":"process","arguments":{"action":"run","data":"Get-ChildItem -Path \"C:\\Users\\28964\\.openclaw\" -Directory | Select-Object Name","timeout":5000}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773556943609}}
