{"type":"message","id":"d1a4b548","parentId":"cbef928d","timestamp":"2026-03-15T06:42:44.951Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"只有一个会话 `agent:main:sysadmin`，但这个会话的 key 看起来是 \"sysadmin\"，但它可能还是绑定到主工作区的。\n\n问题可能是：\n1. 用户创建了 workspace-sysadmin 目录\n2. 但没有正确创建一个绑定到该工作区的会话\n3. 或者 UI 上没有显示切换工作区的选项\n\n我需要帮用户理解：当前对话是在主工作区，所以显示的是 CEO 身份。要用 SysAdmin 身份，需要切换到 workspace-sysadmin 工作区对应的会话。\n\n但看 sessions_list 的结果，只有一个会话，而且它的 sessionId 是 `83a304bd-c07c-43c1-8515-7a84c567546f`。这个会话可能是用 `runtime=\"acp\"` 或其他方式创建的，但不确定它绑定的是哪个工作区。\n\n让我建议用户如何切换到正确的工作区会话，或者帮用户创建一个。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"只有一个会话 (`agent:main:sysadmin`)，但它可能还是绑定在主工作区。\n\n**解决方案：**\n\n你需要一个**绑定到 `workspace-sysadmin` 工作区**的会话。我可以帮你创建一个：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_72323993569e42f6951403a3","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"cwd":"C:\\Users\\28964\\.openclaw\\workspace-sysadmin","label":"sysadmin-workspace","mode":"session","runtime":"subagent","task":"SysAdmin 系统维护员已就绪。工作区：workspace-sysadmin。等待老板指令。","thread":true}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773556958449}}
{"type":"message","id":"543a12b0","parentId":"d1a4b548","timestamp":"2026-03-15T06:42:45.087Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_72323993569e42f6951403a3","toolName":"sessions_spawn","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"error\": \"thread=true is unavailable because no channel plugin registered subagent_spawning hooks.\",\n  \"childSessionKey\": \"agent:main:subagent:f6f20397-10ad-4dbf-9868-483f73a39330\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"error","error":"thread=true is unavailable because no channel plugin registered subagent_spawning hooks.","childSessionKey":"agent:main:subagent:f6f20397-10ad-4dbf-9868-483f73a39330"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773556965082}}
{"type":"message","id":"4d7ee325","parentId":"543a12b0","timestamp":"2026-03-15T06:42:52.685Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"thread=true 不可用，因为当前 channel (webchat) 没有注册 subagent_spawning hooks。但会话还是创建了，只是不是 thread-bound 的。\n\n让我用不带 thread 参数的方式再试一次，或者用 mode=\"run\" 试试。\n\n不过其实更简单的方案是：告诉用户当前情况，以及如何在 UI 里切换到正确的工作区。\n\n实际上，问题可能是 OpenClaw 的 webchat 界面默认只连接到主工作区。要使用 workspace-sysadmin，用户可能需要：\n1. 在 UI 里选择/切换到 workspace-sysadmin\n2. 或者通过某种命令指定工作区\n\n让我先告诉用户当前情况，然后提供一个可行的方案。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"创建遇到了限制（webchat 渠道不支持 thread 模式），但会话已创建。\n\n---\n\n**更直接的方案：**\n\n当前 webchat UI 可能默认只连接主工作区。要使用 `workspace-sysadmin`，你有几个选择：\n\n1. **在 OpenClaw 控制 UI 里切换工作区** — 看看有没有工作区选择器或下拉菜单\n2. **用命令行启动** — `openclaw --workspace workspace-sysadmin`（如果支持）\n3. **让我继续帮你传话** — 我在主工作区，但可以 `sessions_send` 发消息给 sysadmin 会话\n\n**你想用哪种方式？** 或者告诉我你希望怎么配置，我帮你查文档或调整。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773556965088}}
