{"type":"message","id":"3b44b6bd","parentId":"0fe6b719","timestamp":"2026-03-15T06:52:24.117Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"`process` 工具的 `run` 动作也需要 sessionId。让我看看有没有其他方式。\n\n实际上，我可以让用户手动执行这个命令，或者尝试其他方式。\n\n根据文档，Gateway 重启也可以通过发送信号或者调用 API 来完成。但最简单的方式是让用户手动执行命令。\n\n让我告诉用户手动执行重启命令。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"`process` 工具在当前环境下无法直接创建会话执行命令。\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 需要手动执行一步\n\n请在终端运行：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n或者分两步：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway stop\nopenclaw gateway start\n```\n\n---\n\n**重启完成后验证：**\n\n```bash\nopenclaw agents list --bindings\n```\n\n应该看到：\n\n```\nsysadmin  →  webchat:openclaw-control-ui\n```\n\n执行完告诉我，我帮你确认路由是否生效。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773557525835}}
